title: Dog and Beth On The Hunt S02E02 Action In Jackson Part Two WS DS
description:
Description
Dog and Beth continue to help their old friend Jeff Kirkpatrick at Lodise Bail Bonds. They did such a good job of training Dion Shepherd, Jeff Kirkpatrick wants their help with another agent. Nicki McDonald wrote a bad bond for a known runner, and now it's coming back to haunt her. He missed court, and now Nicki has to learn her lesson. Can Dog and Beth show her the ropes and catch Nicki's jump at the same time?
